version_description:
- fix sales deadlock
- minor bug fixes

Wild West Event!

What's new:
Experience the cowboy way of doing business with the Wild West Event!

- Build a Lumber Empire right in the middle of a Wild West and expand overcoming the harsh sunlight heat.
- Hire Sheriffs as new Managers to your factory.
- Complete Event Missions and get valuable Rewards.
- Show everyone who's the boss and win the Unique Prize.
- Enjoy the new surroundings and factory style!
